<p>refer: <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/Jamesbond_/article/details/108148679">https://blog.csdn.net/Jamesbond_/article/details/108148679</a></p>

<p>1.启动(开机）后，按F2进入设置页面，按F2登录，选择Troubleshooting options</p>

<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>

<p>2.回车选择Enable ESXi shell</p>

<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>

<p>右侧ESXi Shell状态已经变为enabled</p>

<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>

<p>保存修改的配置，然后重启，重启之后按Alt+F1，就会进入shell界面，输入用户名密码即可登录</p>

<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>

<p>在命令行按Alt+F2即可切换回界面</p>
